metadata.name: DejaVox Crapauds #1
metadata.description: Your Favourite Crapauds (created from CryptoToadz by Gremplin), got framed and will be your master key to future collections getting released by DejaVox. Hang on the wall of your gallery or virtual space? Or will you be THAT one selling the heirloom to the pawnshop?  Multiple heirlooms incoming for holders of Deja Vox Crapauds.You got Magique ser? Traits released at mint number 10000. Wallets found being part of some form of botting/automation will be excluded from access on future collections even if holding a Crapaud.
